	Component for making screen-savers an easy task<p>

	<b>History : </b><font size=-1><ul>
      <li>09/07/01 - Egg - Fix in PreviewSaver (from Marco Dissel)
      <li>12/04/00 - Egg - Added ssoEnhancedMouseMoveDetection
